## Terms:
- Benga -> Guards / devils
- Bumbo -> spiced rom
- Herras -> currency
- Adrian armada -> the kings fleet

## Saints: (seven held by the church)
- Parlows -> one-armed saint, protector of children and healers
- Douma -> protector of the poor and hardworking
- Liel -> protector of relioguos warriors

